  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of DMT210 Gel, 5% compared
      to vehicle control following 28 days of twice-daily topical application to selected target
      lesions in male and female patients with mild to moderate atopic dermatitis (AD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
