  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male or female 12 years or older

          -  Patient has chronic, stable AD that has been present for at least 3 months with 5-35%
             (inclusive) BSA (Body Surface Area) of AD involvement

          -  Patient has two analogous, Target Lesions; one lesion within each of the two Treatment
             Areas

          -  Patient is willing and able to comply with the protocol

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient has used topical therapies for AD within the Treatment Areas 2 weeks before
             baseline
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
